        "richtext_r87WdC": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>FeraFive was not born in a laboratory.</p><p></p><p>It was born on film sets.</p><p>As a filmmaker, my life has always been fast-paced — unpredictable locations, long shooting hours, changing climates, sleepless nights. In the middle of managing chaos, I began noticing something deeper. Talented women — actors, artists, creators — were constantly struggling with dry skin, dehydration, and body odour caused by harsh lights, constant travel, and environmental changes.</p><p>They were powerful on screen.<br/>But off screen, they were battling their skin.</p><p>And most of them didn’t have the luxury of time for elaborate self-care routines.</p><p>That’s when I asked myself a question:<br/>Why should confident, ambitious women have to choose between chasing their dreams and caring for their skin?</p><p>Instead of depending on what was available in the market, I took it as a personal challenge. I began researching skin hydration, long-lasting freshness, and formulations that could survive changing climates — products that would hydrate deeply, feel luxurious, and keep women fresh through their busiest days.</p><p>That journey led to the creation of FeraFive.</p><p>FeraFive is a premium, clean beauty brand made in India — crafted for women who do it all.<br/>Women who lead meetings, manage homes, attend classes, run businesses, and still show up unapologetically.</p><p>Our formulations are:<br/>• Deeply hydrating<br/>• Designed for long-lasting freshness<br/>• Cruelty-free<br/>• Vegan<br/>• Paraben-free<br/>• Made in India with global standards</p><p>But beyond skincare, FeraFive stands for something greater.</p><p>We believe self-care is not indulgence.<br/>It is power.</p><p>When a woman feels fresh, hydrated, and confident in her skin, she doesn’t just glow — she leads.</p><p>FeraFive is for every woman in Tier 1 cities and beyond who refuses to slow down. For premium buyers who value quality. For those who don’t have time for complicated routines but refuse to compromise on feeling their best.</p><p>This is not just skincare.</p><p>This is confidence in motion.<br/>This is hydration that keeps up with ambition.<br/>This is freshness that lasts as long as her dreams.</p><p>This is FeraFive.</p>"
          }
        }
